ActExport Development Act
PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister for International Trade of MARCELLA SZEL of Calgary, Alberta, as a director of the Board of Directors of Export Development Canada to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, in the place of James A. Pattillo, whose term has expired.
